Add hot (not boiling) water
up to (not over) FILL LEDGE.
2. Stir until well blended.
Microwave uncovered on High 4 to
52 minutes or until tender (sauce will
continue to thicken as it cools).
3. Remove carefully, using both hands.
НOT!
CAUTION: HOT.
Stir; let stand 2 minutes.*
*If you'd like thinner sauce, stir in more hot water, I teaspoon at a time.
HIGH ALTITUDE (3500-6500 ft): After adding hot water to FIlLL LEDGE, add more Tbsp
not water. Stir; microwave uncovered on Medium (50%) 8-9 min. Stir let stand 5 min.
